Cost-utility of a specific collaborative group intervention for patients with 
functional somatic syndromes.

Konnopka A(1), König HH(2), Kaufmann C(3), Egger N(4), Wild B(5), Szecsenyi 
J(6), Herzog W(7), Schellberg D(8), Schaefert R(9).

